dct_title_s: Board of Commerce and Navigation Bridge Openings Newark Bay, Hackensack and Passaic River
dct_description_sm: Map shows the bridge openings along Newark Bay, Hackensack and Passaic River and the various railroads which cross these bodies of water. Towns are labeled and each R.R. lists the size of the opening and the height the bridge is located above mean high water.
